Record Class DocumentedBuilder.ParamInfo

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
io.github.ericmedvet.jnb.core.DocumentedBuilder.ParamInfo
Record Components:
type - the type of the param
enumClass - the (optional) enum class of the param (if any)
name - the name of the param
defaultValue - the (optional) default value of the param
interpolationString - the (optional) interpolation string of the param
injection - an enum saying if the param, when building, has to be filled with special values
javaType - the Java type of the param
Enclosing interface:
DocumentedBuilder<T>
public static record DocumentedBuilder.ParamInfo(ParamMap.Type type, Class<?> enumClass, String name, Object defaultValue, String interpolationString, Param.Injection injection, Type javaType) extends Record
A record storing the information about a param of a DocumentedBuilder.
